oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Woods home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Group photograph of Hugh Bedford Leonard (1875-1899), Katie Mae Burch Leonard (1880-1969), and B. Leonard (b. 1901). Uncle Alfred Moore and Aunt Lindey are posed on either side of the Leonards. The house was built prior to 1849 by Francis Harper Woods of the Belfast community.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houses; Families; Servants
